title: 2016 Week 6 review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 6 review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game breaking down all of the Week 6 action which included a thrilling down-to-the-wire battle between the Seahawks and Falcons, plus a huge upset in Miami as the Dolphins took down the Steelers.
